data.description: Welcome home to this exquisite custom-built, two-story home in the Rice Creek community. This residence features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level. Open concept layout features a formal dining with coffered ceilings and a spacious family room w/ventless gas fireplace. The breakfast nook leads to a chef's kitchen, equipped w/ solid wood cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar w/ seating. Additionally, the main level houses a guest room, full bath, laundry room, and 2-car garage. Upper level features a sophisticated master suite w/ tray ceilings and ensuite bath complete with double sinks, a garden tub, separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms, another full bath, and a media room offer ample space for family and entertainment. Outside, the covered patio overlooks the fenced backyard, providing a setting for outdoor relaxation and gatherings. Schedule your showing today!
